    logout: 'auth_logout',

    authStartLogin: 'auth - Start login',
    authLogin: 'auth - login',
    authStartRegister: 'auth - Start register',
    authStartTokenRenew: 'auth - Start token renew',
    authLogout: 'auth - Logout',
};
